

WHAT GOD IS HE, WRITES LAWS OF PEACE / 他是怎样的神，制定和平的律法

What God is he, writes laws of Peace, / 他是怎样的神，制定和平的律法，
and clothes him in a tempest / 却身披暴风雨
What pitying Angels lusts for Tears, / 怎样的怜悯天使渴望眼泪，
and fans himself with sighs / 并用叹息为自己扇风
What crawling villain preaches abstinence, / 怎样的卑鄙小人宣扬禁欲，
and wraps himself / 却将自己包裹
In fat of Lambs? / 在羔羊的脂肪里？
No more I FOLLOW / 我不再追随
NO MORE OBEDIENCE PAY / 不再顺从


		   
	  
	  
